                    <div class="bbm-calc-chart-caption" id="bbmChartCaption">
                        <em>The pledge path costs more in the early years (cumulative interest premium grows linearly) but pulls ahead once the BTC retained appreciates enough to outpace the premium. The Sell path holds steady at a lower BTC count but carries no interest cost. The crossover year &mdash; if it falls inside your horizon &mdash; is where the math turns.</em>
